sox (Swiss army knife of sound processing),
xsel (command-line tool to access X clipboard and selection buffers),
xscreensaver (Automatic screensaver for X),
mplayer (movie player for Unix-like systems),
pulseaudio (PulseAudio Volume Control),
original-awk (The original awk described in "The AWK Programming Language"),
pkexec (graphical frontend to su),
curl (Get a file from an HTTP, HTTPS or FTP server),
xscreensaver (Automatic screensaver for X),
